interactables.name: Interactable Door 1
dialogue: It seems like everyone in town locks their doors.

interactables.name: Interactable Door 4
dialogue: This is the town inn. Not many travelers stay here, since it's a quiet town.

interactables.name: Interactable Fountain
dialogue: Birds gather on this fountain to bathe sometimes. You have a habit of chasing them away when they group up.

interactables.name: Interactable Gravestone 1
dialogue: You cannot make out any letters on the gravestone, so you cannot tell who died.

interactables.name: Interactable Gravestone 2
dialogue: There's a bouquet of fresh flowers next to the gravestone.

interactables.name: Interactable House Door
dialogue: This is your house. You've lived here for as long as you can remember.
